Access to water is a basic human necessity and it is a human right.  We should not be using access to water as a public utility in which people must pay or lose access.  The government should take over our water and make access to quality drinking water free,

I support Bernie's ban on for-profit charter schools.  Many of these fail our children and when money is the top reason you've opened a school you've already lost the point.  Our children are the top reason and giving them anything less than a quality education shouldn't stand.
